messageBody:
The code is a straightforward combination of Java 1.5 generics with
the delegation pattern. In this case, the delegation is "public"
delegation, where the delegator publicy exposes the delegate. The
delegate that is exposed -- the Node -- is an object capable of
passing a data value of a generic type. This is just a fancy generic
variation on the java "listener" pattern.

Hope this helps.

--jon
